<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'">Quoters shall include a completed copy of 52.212-3 and its ALT I with quotes, if the representation and certification is not available via SAM.gov. All clauses shall be incorporated by reference in the order. Additional contract terms and conditions applicable to this procurement are:</span></p><br />
