<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'">DFARS 252.204-7003, Control of Government Personnel Work Product (April 1992)</span></p><br />
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'">DFARS 252.204-7011,<span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Alternative Line Item Structure (Sept 2011)</span></p><br />
