<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'">Portsmouth Naval Shipyard</span></p><br />
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'">Portsmouth, NH 03801</span></p><br />
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'">All quotes shall include price(s), a point of contact, name and phone number, CAGE Code, business size under NAICS Code 332313, and payment terms. Quotes over 15 pages in total will not be accepted by facsimile. Each response must clearly indicate the capability of the vendor to meet all specifications and requirements.</span></p><br />
<p style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', 'serif'">******* End of Combined Synopsis/Solicitation ********</span></p>


